languages.text: "Мне не по чину комментировать деяния благородных Навис Нобилите... скажу только, что надеюсь, что в следующий визит мы обойдемся без лишних расходов на восстановление числа блюстителей и ремонт".
"It is not my place to comment on the doings of the Navis Nobilite... I will only say that I hope their next visit will not result in the same hefty bill for repairs and enforcer replacements."

languages.text: “我没有资格评论导航宗族的所作所为……我只想说，希望他们下一次拜访时，我们不用再次进行维修，也无需更换执法者。这两方面的开销实在是太大了。”
languages.original_text: "It is not my place to comment on the doings of the Navis Nobilite... I will only say that I hope their next visit will not result in the same hefty bill for repairs and enforcer replacements."

languages.text: « Je n'ai pas à juger les agissements de la Navis Nobilite... J'espère simplement que nous n'aurons pas à dépenser une fortune en réparations et remplacement de personnel lors de leur prochaine visite. »
languages.original_text: "It is not my place to comment on the doings of the Navis Nobilite... I will only say that I hope their next visit will not result in the same hefty bill for repairs and enforcer replacements."

languages.text: «No me corresponde comentar las acciones de la Navis Nobilite... así que me limitaré a desear que la próxima visita no tenga una factura de reparación tan elevada ni conlleve el reemplazo de tantos guardias».
languages.original_text: "It is not my place to comment on the doings of the Navis Nobilite... I will only say that I hope their next visit will not result in the same hefty bill for repairs and enforcer replacements."

languages.text: 「我は航宙貴族の行いについて、とやかく言う立場にありません…ただ、次回の訪問が、また修理とエンフォーサーの補充を求める多額の請求にならないで済むよう祈るばかりです」
